            . I live in Castle-street, Falcon-square. I was between Smithfield and <placeName id="t18330214-157-crimeloc883">St. John's-gate</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18330214-157-crimeloc883" type="placeName" value="St. John's-gate"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18330214-157-crimeloc883" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330214-157-off881 t18330214-157-crimeloc883"></join>, on the 4th of February, about nine o'clock in the evening - I felt my handkerchief being taken from my pocket; I turned, and saw the prisoner crossing the road, perhaps less than twenty yards from me - I gave an alarm; he ran towards Smithfield-bars, where he was stopped - I never lost sight of him; I saw my handkerchief at his feet when he was stopped, about one hundred yards from where I lost it.</p>


